title: HULK SMASH Chronology (HSC) 1962-1965 ZINC
description:
Welcome to the first part of the HULK SMASH chronology, the idea of HULK SMASH chronology is simple to have every issue that the HULK has appeared in be it the main character or with a group of characters then it will be in the HULK SMASH chronology.
This pack is complied from different sources so credit goes to the original scanners and up-loaders
